<h1>22. A stroll beside Pontsticill Reservoir</h1>
<div class="article-video right clearfix"/>
<p/><div class="documentDescription">
<span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span kukitmark="1" class="kssattr-atfieldname-description kssattr-templateId-widgets/textarea kssattr-macro-textarea-field-view inlineEditable" id="parent-fieldname-description">The reservoir is surrounded by hills and forests in the Taf Fechan Valley in the central Brecon Beacons.</span></span></span></span></div>
