<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>Further Information</strong></span></span></span><br/>Â </div>
<div>
<span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">This is a popular area and is a good site for watching birds. The Brecon Mountain Railway and Merthyr Tydfil Sailing Club are on the eastern side of the reservoir. There are several places to park by the road side on the western side of the reservoir, including one car park with a sloped and grassy path to a picnic area.</span></span></span><br/>Â </div>
<div>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>How to get there:</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">This site is located next to a minor road 3 miles north-east of Merthyr Tydfil.</span></span></span><br/>
<br/>Â </div>
<div>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>Nearest town or village:</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Pontsticill.</span></span></span><br/>
<br/>Â </div>
<div>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>OS Grid Reference:</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Explorer Map OL12 or Landranger Map 160 â€“
<strong>SO 053 127.</strong></span></span></span><br/>
<br/>Â </div>
<div>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>Distance:</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Up to 2 miles along the road â€“ please note this road can be busy at weekends.</span></span></span><br/>
<br/>Â </div>
<div>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>Contact:</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Welsh Water on 01495 769281.</span></span></span><br/>
<br/>Â </div>
<div>
<span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><strong>Facilities</strong>:</span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);">There are several pubs in the area but the nearest facilities are at Merthyr Tydfil. Sailing: Merthyr Tydfil Sailing Club can accommodate disabled people on their boats. Enquiries should be addressed to Mrs Govier, 43 Hatherleigh Road, Cardiff, CF3 9AS or telephone 029 20 778459. Fishing information can be obtained from Merthyr Tydfil Angling Association (</span><a kukitmark="1" href="http://www.mtaa.co.uk"><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);">www.mtaa.co.uk</span></a><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);">).</span></span></span><br/>
<br/>Â </div>
<div>
<span style="color: rgb(51, 153, 0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>Parking:</strong></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">There are several small roadside lay-bys and car parks alongside the reservoir. These are mainly compacted stone and can be uneven.</span></span></span><br/>
